  "body": "``` sh\n> npm test\n\n> instantsearch.js@0.0.1 test /home/vvo/Dev/Algolia/instantsearch.js\n> babel-node test/*.js && npm run lint\n\nTAP version 13\n# InstantSearch\nok 1 algoliasearch called\nok 2 algoliasearch(appId, apiKey)\nok 3 algoliasearchHelper not yet called\nok 4 widget.getConfiguration called\nok 5 widget.getConfiguration(current searchParameters)\nok 6 algoliasearchHelper called\nok 7 algoliasearchHelper(merged searchParameters)\nok 8 helper.search called\nok 9 widget.init called\nok 10 widget.init called after widget.getConfiguration\nok 11 widget.init(helper.state, helper)\nok 12 widget.render not yet called\nok 13 widget.render called\nok 14 widget.render(results, state, helper)\n\n1..14\n# tests 14\n# pass  14\n\n# ok\n\n\n> instantsearch.js@0.0.1 lint /home/vvo/Dev/Algolia/instantsearch.js\n> ./scripts/lint.sh\n\n\nLint\n```\n",
